wyvern.tools.typedAST.core.expressions

Class TaggedInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • wyvern.tools.typedAST.core.expressions.TaggedInfo

  • public class TaggedInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class encapsulates information about what tags a type is a case of and what comprises it.
    Author:
    Troy Shaw, Alex and Ben fixed it all up after merge in GIT failed :-)
